@baseUrl = https://geekzkai.onrender.com/api

### 👤 Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "itachi",
  "email": "itachi@example.com",
  "passwordHash": "sharingan"
}

###

### 👤 Create Another User
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "naruto",
  "email": "naruto@example.com",
  "passwordHash": "rasengan"
}

###

### 📜 Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/user

###

### 👤 Get Single User
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/1

###

### 📝 Create Post (User 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What if Naruto joined the Akatsuki?",
  "description": "Would the Leaf still survive?",
  "userId": 1
}

###

### 📝 Create Another Post (User 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What if Itachi never died?",
  "description": "How would the Uchiha clan evolve?",
  "userId": 2
}

###

### 📜 Get All Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/post

###

### 📜 Get Post by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/post/1

###

